* Zyber stretched again as she looked across the fire at 
Blaster(DeathScythe), looking over him to see if he really was alright. She 
had to admit if nothing else that he was rather a unique creature, looking 
as if he had scanned every animal, fish, insect, and bird on the planet when 
he had landed.
But even if he was not quite praportioned right, he was still a rather nice 
bot none the less.
She smiles as he answeres her.*

" That is good. I was not sure whether or not that salve would work on a bot 
with as much power as you. I have only used it on myself before."

*Zyber lay back down onto her stomach as she watched Blaster look into the 
fire and then turn his eyes back at her, though watching every one of his 
moves.
She was way to trustworthy, she knew that. And she trusted sometimes when it 
could be the worst thing for her.
But she simply nodded as he thanked her for saving his life, but then looked 
at him point blank when he asked for her to fill in more information for her 
on tis planet.
However, that was information with which she could give.*

" There is a bit."

* Through her scouting and such she had come to know quite a bit, but why 
this Blaster would want to know was beyond her.*

" There is a new Maximal ship, the Cybertronian Fire. Which is located in 
the plains of Africa.
There is a new leader for the Predacons.
Other then that there are other battles but nothing too seriouse.
Iron Raptor is leading the Maximals.
The winds are changing and the herds are moving south, leaving almost no 
food in the north here.
The enire planet is changing in fact, climate, sea level. But nothing out of 
the ordinery."

* Zyber then stretched again and yawned a bit.*

" Is there anything specific you would like to know?"
